                        modelFields="[text@richtext]"
                        name="Text Container Text"
                        text="&lt;p>In accordance with the provisions of the Accounting Act (Official Gazette No. 85/24, 145/24), which implements Directive (EU) 2021/2101 of the European Parliament and of the Council of 24 November 2021 amending Directive 2013/34/EU as regards the disclosure of income tax information by certain undertakings and branches (OJ L 429, 1.12.2021), AbbVie d.o.o. has prepared a Report on Income Tax Information. The aforementioned Report on Income Tax Information is publicly available on the website of the Annual Financial Statements Register at the following link:&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;p>&lt;a href=&quot;https://rgfi.fina.hr/JavnaObjava-web/jsp/prijavaKorisnika.jsp&quot;>https://rgfi.fina.hr/JavnaObjava-web/jsp/prijavaKorisnika.jsp&lt;/a>&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;p>U skladu s odredbama Zakona o računovodstvu (Narodne novine br. 85/24., 145/24) kojima je implementirana Direktiva (EU) 2021/2101 Europskog parlamenta i Vijeća od 24. studenoga 2021. o izmjeni Direktive 2013/34/EU u pogledu objavljivanja informacija o porezu na dobit koje provode određena poduzeća i podružnice (SL L 429, 1. 12. 2021.), AbbVie d.o.o. je pripremio Izvještaj o informacijama o porezu na dobit. Navedeni Izvještaj o informacijama o porezu na dobit javno je&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;p>dostupan na internetskoj stranici Registra godišnjih financijskih izvještaja, na sljedećoj poveznici:&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;p>&lt;a href=&quot;https://rgfi.fina.hr/JavnaObjava-web/jsp/prijavaKorisnika.jsp&quot;>https://rgfi.fina.hr/JavnaObjava-web/jsp/prijavaKorisnika.jsp&lt;/a>&lt;/p>"/>
